<h2>Virginia Tech climate action and sustainability plan</h2>
<p>In the plan, Virginia Tech affirms its commitment to reducing campus greenhouse gas emissions to 80 percent below its 1990 emission level by 2050.</p><a href="http://www.facilities.vt.edu/sustainability/">Learn More.</a></div>
